                        handle,
                        ciphertext,
                        ciphertext_version,
                        ciphertext_type,
                        input_blob_hash,
                        input_blob_index

                    VALUES($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                    ON CONFLICT (handle, ciphertext_version) DO NOTHING
